Commercial Application Overview 

The product model underpins all the business processes used in the Auto line of business. This line of business offers two products namely Multi Auto and Commercial Auto.

This diagram shows the product model for the Multi Auto root product at a high level:
This diagram shows the product model for the Commercial Auto root product at a high level:

Multi Auto Product Model
The Multi Auto product is a multi-instance product model that lets users create quotes for multiple vehicles driven by multiple drivers. This product model has the flexibility to handle complex combinations, such as a quote that's got three vehicles and four drivers who aren't all associated with the same vehicles.

Commercial Auto Product Model
The Commercial Auto product is a single-instance product model that lets businesses create quotes for multiple vehicles from a single location.
